summary: This MOD replace the running and walking animation.
descriptionHtml:
Boku no kangaeta saikyou no hokou to soukou anime-shon.
(Meaning : This MOD replace female running and walking animation)

[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mvCxNefXT3s]Female sprint animation v1.31[/url]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hmkkOHFd1UU]Female sprint animation v1.33[/url]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1nMMBC6C-qQ]Female sprint animation v1.41[/url]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QTzTMbbYpPU]Female sprint animation v1.42[/url]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F7Vxb8j5n0Y]Female sprint animation v1.44[/url]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N7Dfj0CB8nA]Female running animation v1.45[/url]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=znY04wjcuYs]Female idle animation v1.51[/url]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZvt7PDp8vA]Female idle animation v1.32[/url]

======= Required ==========================================================
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800]XP32 Maximum Skeleton -XPMS[/url] or [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68000]XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended - XPMSE[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11811]Fores New Idles in Skyrim - FNIS[/url]

======= Note ==============================================================
It may bit bounce BBP animation by the body mesh MOD. If you don't use the backward walking and running speedup MOD, you'll get results that are not good. The MOD has cloak animation, but I have not tested it.

Figment, fore, XP32, kamo1, Groovtama, Thank you for great MOD and tools!
